node.text:
#BIRTHDAYBOY 💚

Thank you everyone for the lovely bday wishes. I’m officially 30!! I feel like you all have watched me grow up on social media & achieve my dreams. I am forever grateful for all of your consistent support over the years. I had a really beautiful day surrounded by people I love and feel truly blessed to see another year of life. I can’t wait to see what this new chapter will bring and I hope you will all be here to witness what’s to come. I love you all 💫
